  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a very bad time, also, socially.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People didn't trust each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Each one-- everybody start-- started to-- to look out for himself only, to try to grab something to eke out just a sheer livelihood.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The question of starvation is one of the most demeaning questions-- when suddenly, everything else goes into the background, and you cannot get rid of the idea-- food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time-- I don't recall a time without anti-Semitism in any form or another.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is an endemic disease-- endemic disease that has accompanied the lives of the Europeans, and many other countries too, for the past 2,000 years.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, one has to-- it was not-- of course, it became worse, because they-- there was this part of-- of so-called intellectual Europe that started to blame the Jews for the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you have to find-- there was a comic-- a German comic in Munich who said about the anti-Semitism, it's-- it's-- it's the Jews and the bicyclists who are to be blamed.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and he was asked-- this was on stage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was asked why-- because there are too many of them anywhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
